description: If you're looking for food that makes you feel real good, there's always a place for you at Alice's Comfort Table. This savory selection of family recipes is absolutely sure to please, no matter what you’re craving. Their offerings include oh-so-scrumptious Pork Belly Grilled Cheese, big ole’ BBQ Meatloaf Sandwiches, and delicious Chicken Pot Pie. For all this and much more, be sure to come by Alice's Comfort Table!
name: Alice's Comfort Table
